questions.statement:
Two sets of numbers are given below. In each set of numbers, certain mathematical operation(s) on the first number result(s) in the second number. Similarly, certain mathematical operation(s) on the second number result(s) in the third number and so on. Which of the given options follows the same set of operations as in the given sets?&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
(NOTE: Operations should be performed on the whole numbers, without breaking down the numbers into their constituent digits. E.g., 13 &amp;ndash; Operations on 13 such as adding/subtracting/multiplying to 13 can be performed. Breaking down 13 into 1 and 3 and then performing mathematical operations on 1 and 3 is not allowed.)&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
14 &amp;ndash; 196 &amp;ndash; 186 &amp;ndash; 172 ; 15 &amp;ndash; 225 &amp;ndash; 215 &amp;ndash; 200<br>ਸੰਖਿਆਵਾਂ ਦੇ ਦੋ ਸੈੱਟ ਹੇਠਾਂ ਦਿੱਤੇ ਗਏ ਹਨ। ਸੰਖਿਆਵਾਂ ਦੇ ਹਰੇਕ ਸੈੱਟ ਵਿੱਚ, ਪਹਿਲੀ ਸੰਖਿਆ 'ਤੇ ਕੁਝ ਗਣਿਤਿਕ ਕਿਰਿਆ(ਵਾਂ) ਦਾ ਨਤੀਜਾ ਦੂਜੀ ਸੰਖਿਆ ਹੁੰਦਾ ਹੈ। ਇਸੇ ਤਰ੍ਹਾਂ, ਦੂਜੀ ਸੰਖਿਆ 'ਤੇ ਕੁਝ ਗਣਿਤਿਕ ਕਿਰਿਆ(ਵਾਂ) ਦਾ ਨਤੀਜਾ ਤੀਜੀ ਸੰਖਿਆ ਹੁੰਦਾ ਹੈ ਅਤੇ ਇਸੇ ਤਰ੍ਹਾਂ ਅੱਗੇ। ਦਿੱਤੇ ਗਏ ਵਿਕਲਪਾਂ ਵਿੱਚੋਂ ਕਿਹੜਾ ਦਿੱਤੇ ਗਏ ਸੈੱਟਾਂ ਦੇ ਓਪਰੇਸ਼ਨਾਂ ਦੇ ਸਮਾਨ ਸੈੱਟ ਦੀ ਪਾਲਣਾ ਕਰਦਾ ਹੈ?<br />
<br />
(ਨੋਟ: ਓਪਰੇਸ਼ਨ ਪੂਰਨ ਸੰਖਿਆਵਾਂ 'ਤੇ ਕੀਤੇ ਜਾਣੇ ਚਾਹੀਦੇ ਹਨ, ਸੰਖਿਆਵਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਉਹਨਾਂ ਦੇ ਸੰਘਟਕ ਅੰਕਾਂ ਵਿੱਚ ਵੰਡਣ ਤੋਂ ਬਿਨਾਂ। ਉਦਾਹਰਨ ਲਈ, 13 - 13 'ਤੇ ਓਪਰੇਸ਼ਨ ਜਿਵੇਂ ਕਿ 13 ਵਿੱਚ ਜੋੜਨਾ/ਘਟਾਉਣਾ/ਗੁਣਾ ਕਰਨਾ ਕੀਤਾ ਜਾ ਸਕਦਾ ਹੈ। 13 ਨੂੰ 1 ਅਤੇ 3 ਵਿੱਚ ਵੰਡਣਾ ਅਤੇ ਫਿਰ 1 ਅਤੇ 3 'ਤੇ ਗਣਿਤਿਕ ਓਪਰੇਸ਼ਨ ਕਰਨਾ ਮਨਜ਼ੂਰ ਨਹੀਂ ਹੈ।)<br />
<br />
14 - 196 - 186 - 172 ; 15 - 225 - 215 - 200

questions.explanation:
&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;The logic followed here is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;14 &amp;ndash; 196 &amp;ndash; 186 &amp;ndash; 172&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;14&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 196 &amp;rarr; 196 - 10 = 186&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 186 - 14 = 172&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;And,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;15 &amp;ndash; 225 &amp;ndash; 215 &amp;ndash; 200&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;15&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 225 &amp;rarr; 225 - 10 = 215 &amp;rarr; 215 - 15 = 200&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So, checking each option one by one:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;9 &amp;ndash; 81 &amp;ndash; 71 &amp;ndash; 62&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;9&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 81 &amp;rarr; 81 - 10 = 71 &amp;rarr; 71&amp;nbsp;- 9 = 62&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 2)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;3 &amp;ndash; 9 &amp;ndash; 19 &amp;ndash; 14&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;3&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 9 &amp;rarr; 9 - 10 = (-1)&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; (-1)&amp;nbsp;- 3 = (-4)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;&amp;ne; 14&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 3)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;8 &amp;ndash; 64 &amp;ndash; 54 &amp;ndash; 40&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;8&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 64 &amp;rarr; 64 - 10 = 54 &amp;rarr; 54 - 8 = 46&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;&amp;ne; 40&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 4)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;6 &amp;ndash; 36 &amp;ndash; 26 &amp;ndash; 22&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;6&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 36 &amp;rarr; 36 - 10 = 26 &amp;rarr; 26 - 6 = 20&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;&amp;ne; 22&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Thus, out of all the options, &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;9 &amp;ndash; 81 &amp;ndash; 71 &amp;ndash; 62&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;&amp;#39; follows the same logic as given.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;Hence,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 1&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is the correct answer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">ਇੱਥੇ ਲਾਗੂ ਕੀਤਾ ਗਿਆ ਤਰਕ ਹੈ:</p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">14 - 196 - 186 - 172</p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);"><span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">14<sup>2</sup></span><span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);"> = 196 &rarr; 196 - 10 = 186 &rarr; 186 - 14 = 172 </span></p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">ਅਤੇ,</p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">15 - 225 - 215 - 200</p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);"><span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">15<span style="position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;">2</span></span><span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);"> = 225 &rarr; 225 - 10 = 215 &rarr; 215 - 15 = 200</span></p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">ਇਸ ਲਈ, ਹਰੇਕ ਵਿਕਲਪ ਦੀ ਇੱਕ-ਇੱਕ ਕਰਕੇ ਜਾਂਚ ਕਰਨਾ:</p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">ਵਿਕਲਪ 1) <span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">9 - 81 - 71 - 62</span></p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);"><span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">9<span style="position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; font-size:10.5px;">2</span></span><span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);"> = 81 &rarr; 81 - 10 = 71 &rarr; 71 - 9 = 62</span></p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">ਵਿਕਲਪ 2) <span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">3 - 9 - 19 - 14</span></p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);"><span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">3<span style="position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; font-size:10.5px;">2</span> = 9 &rarr; 9 - 10 = (-1) &rarr; (-1) - 3 = (-4) </span><span style="color:  (32, 33, 36);">&ne; 14</span></p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">ਵਿਕਲਪ 3) <span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">8 - 64 - 54 - 40</span></p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);"><span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">8<span style="position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; font-size:10.5px;">2</span> = 64 &rarr; 64 - 10 = 54 &rarr; 54 - 8 = 46 </span><span style="color:  (32, 33, 36);">&ne; 40</span></p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">ਵਿਕਲਪ 4) <span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">6 - 36 - 26 - 22</span></p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);"><span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">6<span style="position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; font-size:10.5px;">2</span> = 36 &rarr; 36 - 10 = 26 &rarr; 26 - 6 = 20 </span><span style="color:  (32, 33, 36);">&ne; 22</span></p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">ਇਸ ਤਰ੍ਹਾਂ, ਸਾਰੇ ਵਿਕਲਪਾਂ ਵਿੱਚੋਂ, '<span style="color:  (33, 37, 41);">9 - 81 - 71 - 62</span><span style="font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);">' ਦਿੱਤੇ ਗਏ ਤਰਕ ਦੀ ਪਾਲਣਾ ਕਰਦਾ ਹੈ।</span></p>

<p style="color:  (33, 37, 41);"><span style="font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);">ਇਸ ਲਈ, <span style="font-weight: bolder;">"ਵਿਕਲਪ 1"</span> ਸਹੀ ਉੱਤਰ ਹੈ।</span></p>

