&lt;p&gt;Given Alphabets:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;M O V E O I F V A S K C O S D V I N S D I N I S&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Consonants are immediately preceded by a vowel and also immediately followed by a vowel,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So, the pattern should be:&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/03/F2_Savita_Railways_22-3-23_D28.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 219px; height: 27px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now,&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/03/F2_Savita_Railways_22-3-23_D27.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 470px; height: 32px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So, there are Two pairs i.e.: &amp;#39;OVE&amp;#39; and &amp;#39;INI&amp;#39;.&lt;/p&gt;

