&lt;p&gt;In a certain code language,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;#39;A + B means &amp;lsquo;A is the son of B&amp;rsquo;,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;#39;A &amp;minus; B means &amp;lsquo;A is the brother of B&amp;rsquo;,&lt;/p&gt;

